WEBVTT

00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:30.931
(TED Talk) Bill Gates:
If you go into a country

00:00:30.955 --> 00:00:34.308
with the right tools and the right way,
and you do it vigorously,

00:00:34.332 --> 00:00:37.070
you can actually get a local eradication.

00:00:37.490 --> 00:00:39.293
CA: Empowering teachers.

00:00:39.317 --> 00:00:42.317
(TED Talk) BG: Diagnosing areas
where a teacher needs to improve

00:00:42.341 --> 00:00:43.834
is only half the battle.

00:00:44.488 --> 00:00:48.368
We also have to give them the tools
they need to act on the diagnosis.

00:00:48.789 --> 00:00:52.577
If you learn that you need to improve
the way you teach fractions,

00:00:52.601 --> 00:00:54.895
you should be able to watch a video

00:00:54.919 --> 00:00:57.988
of the best person in the world
teaching fractions.

00:00:58.395 --> 00:01:00.995
CA: And the quest for renewable energy.